snippet.title: Hellementalz -  Prototype Trailer
snippet.description:
Hype the game at IGDB: https://www.igdb.com/games/hellementalz

In Hellementalz you have  the elements under your control. Throw fireballs from your hands, use huge rocks to protect yourself and destroy the environment around you.

Hellementalz is currently work in progress.

-

Website: www.loneherostudios.com/games/hellementalz/
